observations.recommendation:
4.9.1 Immediately comply with the submission of the documents and reports mentioned;
4.9.2 Impose the suspension of payment of salaries of the Accountable Officers who repeatedly failed to submit the documents and reports mentioned above within the prescribed period, as mandated in Section 122 of P.D. No. 1445; and
4.9.3 Be mindful, on pain of an administrative disciplinary action, under Section 127 of P.D. No. 1445 which states that unjustified failure of a public officer to comply with any of the provision of PD No. 1445 shall constitute neglect of duty.
